{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM05_ST4_620.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x39,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "When I synthesized the Flower Oil,<CR>I fell asleep..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "And before I knew it, I was with Nio at some place I've never seen before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "After I woke up, I thought that maybe it could've just been a dream, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I gave Nio her favorite candy in the dream, and when I woke up, I didn't have it anymore."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I don't know how it worked, but I was able to give Nio an object."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... So you're saying...that in a dream-like space, you were able to meet your sister, and give her an object?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I know it may not sound believable, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "No, it's not impossible."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Perhaps it follows the same principle as the tool I used to move us from the village to the library..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "But Nio also said that she couldn't open the bag of candy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "So physical contact wasn't possible. A conclusion that could be derived from that would be..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x92,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Your sister is likely in a state of being where her mind and body are distinctly separated."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Her body is most likely in a dormant condition. What you've been meeting with was her astral body."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Now that I think about it, it did kinda feel like she didn't have a physical presence..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Oh, and one more thing. A while back, my friend's calf went missing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Then, flowers near a ruin suddenly started to bloom, and I thought I saw the calf bathed in light..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "And the calf totally disappeared into the light!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "That's most likely a transport technique. They're used to transmit objects over vast distances."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "There's more to this story.<CR>So, the calf comes back..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "And when it does, there are two of them! Two of the same calf came back! Isn't that amazing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "That's a common mistake with transport techniques. I've done it many times in the past, myself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "*gasp* Then if something went wrong when we came to the library, there could've been two of me, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Relax. The one I'm using now is very stable. The odds of something happening with this one are 10,000 to 1."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Then that means...there's still a possibility of something happening once every 10,000 times...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "*gulp* Now I'm starting to get nervous."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, to be able to send something from this side is an interesting development."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Knowing that, we may be able to take an effective step forward."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "I have one idea, but first, let's hear your opinion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "What would you do now?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Well, I think it'd be nice to be able to find the sent object."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x16c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... Using what kind of method?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Umm, it's starting to feel like I'm taking some kind of test..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x16d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Don't worry about that. Continue."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "For example, if I send something that creates sound, I could use the sound to look for Nio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "The \"words\" emitted from the Flower<CR>Crystal...were able to confuse the<CR>slags from very far away..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "So if I can make something like that and send it to the other side..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x16d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "That is roughly correct. Let's proceed according to that plan."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x16d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Now, we should start by creating this \"object\" to send to the other side."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x16d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "I shall give you a hint for the basic principles. After that, you must create it on your own..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x16e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "And with it, gracefully locate that thing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Uh, Mr. Keith, you're not gonna help me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "You've come this far. Wouldn't you like to accomplish the rest on your own?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "Haha...well...I guess..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "You don't need to worry. When you're going against that thing, I'll lend you a hand, to some extent."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "Oh, you will!? Th-That's really reassuring..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "Then, don't think about unnecessary things and just focus on attaining your goal."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "msg_string": "The path has already been laid out before you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "msg_string": "You're right. I need to put all my effort into this...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "msg_string": "Um, Mr. Keith, thank you very much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x31,
            "msg_string": "What's with you all of a sudden?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x32,
            "msg_string": "Well, after all, I just thought I've been depending on your assistance."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x33,
            "msg_string": "...Gratitude is unnecessary.<CR>I'm merely doing these things<CR>to satisfy my own interests."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x34,
            "msg_string": "That is all. Farewell."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x35,
            "msg_string": "(Mr. Keith always ends up helping me...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x36,
            "msg_string": "(I guess...he really is a nice person, huh?)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You learned how to make the Slag Transmitter."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Keithgriff can now join your party."
        }
    ]
}